text: Jamie Luis Gomez (born July 14, 1975), better known by his stage name Taboo, is an American rapper, singer, songwriter, actor and DJ. He is best known as a member of the hip hop music group The Black Eyed Peas. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:American DJs Category:American hip hop musicians Category:Rappers from California Category:American songwriters Category:Musicians from Los Angeles Category:Black Eyed Peas members
